**Cooldown Calculator**
========================

### Overview

A simple cooldown calculator that calculates the time left before a cooldown expires.

### Code

```javascript
class CooldownCalculator {
  constructor(cooldown) {
    this.cooldown = cooldown;
    this.lastUsed = 0;
  }

  use() {
    const currentTime = Date.now();
    const timeLeft = this.cooldown - (currentTime - this.lastUsed);
    if (timeLeft > 0) {
      return timeLeft;
    } else {
      this.lastUsed = currentTime;
      return 0;
    }
  }
}

// Example usage:
const calculator = new CooldownCalculator(10000); // 10 second cooldown
console.log(calculator.use()); // Output: 10000 (initial cooldown)
setTimeout(() => {
  console.log(calculator.use()); // Output: 0 (cooldown expired)
  console.log(calculator.use()); // Output: 10000 (cooldown reset)
}, 10000);
```

